meta_keywords: wedding blog inspiration photography design wedding ideas themes professional blogger uk magazine bridal trends bridesmaids style blogging
data.meta_description: Wedding inspiration for unique brides. Featuring amazing wedding photography and the latest bridal themes Rock n Roll Bride provides a little haven of kick-ass weddingness in a cookie-cutter, pastel and often puke-worthy wedding world. If you've ever picked up a bridal magazine and felt disheartened by what you didn't find well, my friend, you are in the right place!
data.text:
Bright & Sunny Yellow + Pink Wedding Editorial with a $30 Budget

Kat

The Villar Photo Co.

If you picked up a copy of the latest issue of the magazine, then you will have already seen a preview of this incredible yellow wedding session. We loved the photos so much we felt they deserved a full feature in all it's sunny and bright glory too!
